    "updated_at": "2016-03-31T09:14:48Z",
    "body": "> I was originally hoping to make this an argument on the actual dialog.show\\* calls, but it seems the parameter set is defined in libchromiumcontent and I wasn't sure it would be appropriate to add there?\n\nThe parameter is parsed at `atom/browser/ui/message_box_mac.mm` and `file_dialog_mac.mm` in electron, we can add it there.\n"
