    "created_at": "2016-04-16T15:23:54Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-16T15:23:54Z",
    "body": "It might make more sense to put this API on the BrowserWindow, since all the other window sizing / metrics methods are there, and it'd never really make sense to call it on a window other than the current one.\n\nGoing to change the API to this, if it seems reasonable:\n\n```\nconst toolbarRect = document.getElementById('toolbar').getBoundingClientRect()\nremote.getCurrentWindow().setSheetOffset(toolbarRect.height)\n```\n"
  },
